{"tid":694131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[垃圾IT]Facebook再爆私隱漏洞 只供私人瀏覽的帖文，全被自動設定為公眾帖文","createTime":"2018-06-08T05:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T06:34:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7dfdf0c647669e165d45bfc2644b6aa1b60d0d","tid":694131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"繼「劍橋分析」違規收集Facebook用戶資料後，Facebook再涉私隱醜聞。Facebook於美國時間周四承認，用戶於上月18至27日期間於Facebook上發布<span style=\"color: red;\">只供朋友瀏覽的私人帖文時，全被自動設定為公眾帖文，容許所有人瀏覽，估計1400萬名用戶受影響。</span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook發聲明承認問題，他們向CNN承認，在上月18日測試新功能已出現問題，在22日已修正問題，但直到27日才完全堵截漏洞。若然當時用戶的帖文變為公開帖文，Facebook指他們已助用家變回原有設定。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Facebook會沿用用戶上次帖文的設定，如當用戶上載相片，並設為朋友才可瀏覽，下次再發帖文時，Facebook會沿用上次的設定，即設定為朋友才可瀏覽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2090550/Facebook%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E3%80%801400%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2090550%2FFacebook%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E%25E3%2580%25801400%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF&d=akJa0BhxT1CBrAKZ%2F%2FudKS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a3cf1b70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2090550/Facebook%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E3%80%801400%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF</a>"},{"pid":"243701ead50233260afb6ae176de8f4d8597452e","tid":694131,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97916b48dbfdf408ba08f24de00992404edf6067","tid":694131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"一早知佢多bug,佢d setting亂到X，又成日改版<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇bu